summary.name: Home Depot Distribution Centers in the US
summary.description:
List of Home Depot Distribution Centers in the US.

DFC: Direct Fufillment Center; RDC: Rapid Deployment Center; FDC: Flatbed Distribution Center; BDC: Bulk Distribution Center; IFC: Internal Freight Consolidation; MDO: Market Delivery Operations; SDC: Stocking Distribution Center

Samuel Fleischman, "Home Depot Distribution Centers in the US," Manifest: Supply Chain Platform (2024)
